definition: name of the product associated with the feature, e.g. the mRNA of an mRNA feature, the polypeptide of a CDS, the mature peptide of a mat_peptide, etc.
example: /product="trypsinogen" (when qualifier appears in CDS feature) /product="trypsin" (when qualifier appears in mat_peptide feature) /product="XYZ neural-specific transcript" (when qualifier appears in mRNA feature)
